There's more than meets the eye in the case of Mario Lee, but if there's anything you should know it's that he's incisive and curious. Of course he's also punctual, lovable and honorable, but they're tainted by and mixed with habits of being crazy as well. His incisive nature though, this is what he's most well-liked for. Friends usually count on this and his relaxed nature whenever they need help. Nobody's perfect of course and Mario has less pleasant traits too. His thievish nature and disrespectful nature can cause things to heat up and reach all around. Fortunately his curiosity assures this isn't the case very often.

Many things can be said of Rachel Phillips, but most know that above all else she's decisive and cooperative. Of course she's also spontaneous, persuasive and intelligent, but they're tainted by and mixed with habits of being hostile as well. Her decisive nature though, this is what she's most well-liked for. People often count on this and her independence in times of need. Nobody's perfect of course and Rachel has a fair share of lesser days too. Her power-hungry ways and pompous nature risk ruining pleasant moods and just affect all around negatively. Fortunately her cooperation shines brighter on most days.

It takes a while to get to know Allison Jenkins, but above else know that she's considerate and tolerant. Of course she's also honorable, intuitive and idealistic, but they're less prominent and often intertwined with being tactless as well. Her considerate nature though, this is what she's often admired for. Friends tend to count on this and her honor when they're in need of support. Nobody's perfect of course and Allison has a fair share of lesser days too. Her disruptive nature and aggression cause plenty of grievances even at the best of times. Fortunately her tolerance helps make sure these days are few and far between.
